{
  "stem": "20035.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was around 25, 30 miles west of Budapest-- southwest of Budapest, called Kistercsa, K-I-S-T-E-R-C-S-A.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was-- I assume-- I never heard about this place before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Naturally, as a kid, I didn't hear about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was an internment camp for prisoners, prisoners who were not ready yet, probably before sentencing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was an internment camp, fully walled and barbed wire and guarded, and guard houses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I mean, it was-- was a camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every-- not for Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was-- this was a prisoner internment-- internment camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But by the time we get there, there was nobody there but Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was there for a period of approximately over a month.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Way over a month.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because by-- by knowing what's happening, well, probably closer to two months, five or six weeks before, once again, we were able to let dad-- mom and dad know that we are there.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's the place when probably the-- the service or the-- the-- the position, what my dad had in the Hungarian Army, served.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because he found an officer, an army officer who was willing-- and we found out, naturally for a lot of money, he was willing to risk and come.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And suddenly there was one of the-- one of the prison guards came and looked for the two Gottliebs, Louis and George Gottleib.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had no idea where, what and how.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Suddenly this Hungarian officer signed something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the two of us left with the officer, who never said two words to us, not two words.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He-- where we are going, what we are doing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were out of that camp in his car.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a rickety old car.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And drove us to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
